videos.description: Arizona State guard Kodi Justice gives the Sun Devils an 11-point lead after making back-to-back steals with two buckets.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Sun Devils' Justice forces back-to-back steals) 2018/01/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Sun Devils' Justice forces back-to-back steals

videos.description: Utah forward David Collette grabs the pass from Justin Bibbins and throws down a slam from the baseline.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Utes goes baseline for slam) 2018/01/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Utes goes baseline for slam

videos.description: Sun Devils freshman Remy Martin drives through traffic and connects with dazzling finger roll lay-in.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Arizona State freshman hits nasty finger roll) 2018/01/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Arizona State freshman hits nasty finger roll

videos.description: Utah's Justin Bibbins knocks down a 3-pointer then Arizona State guard Shannon Evans II answers with his own long distance triple.

tracking.trackingName: NCB_One-Play (Utes, Sun Devils hit back-to-back 3's) 2018/01/07 ESHEET

videos.headline: Utes, Sun Devils hit back-to-back 3's

videos.description: Utah turns over the ball and Arizona State quickly transitions for a Shannon Evans II 3-pointer.
videos.headline: Sun Devils hit transition 3

videos.description: Utah guard Justin Bibbins works with 14 seconds remaining and puts up a 3-pointer that looks good, but goes in and out of the bucket, losing to Arizona State in a close game.
